{"tid":2261421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國女學生不站立尊敬國旗，路邊大媽當場揮拳痛毆！","createTime":"2020-10-28T09:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T08:56:41.000Z","uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"26b83f63cdb9d8b89303c5eec17bcd92135cc096","tid":2261421,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">泰國女學生不站立尊敬國旗，路邊大媽當場毆打女學生！</span></strong><br />\n2020年10月28日 - by 知否<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201028151348-735x400.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201028151348-735x400.png&h=b2eaa947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊據泰媒10月28日報導，近日有一則中年大媽毆打女學生的視頻在網上瘋傳，視頻中有2名女學生在大城府火車站內坐著，突然有位中年大媽就打了其中一名女學生，並且大媽口中還振振有詞稱：&ldquo;是不是泰國學生，還穿著校服！&rdquo; 另據分享視頻作者透露，<span class=\"red\">這位大媽之所以打女學生，原因是女學生不願意站立起來尊重國旗。</span><br />\n<br />\n而經了解，事後被打女學生已經向警方報案，並且被送往醫院檢查身體。至於女學生被打的原因，初步調查得知，事發當天下午18：00，女學生由於來月經，所以沒有站立起來尊重國旗，沒想到卻因此受了大媽的打和謾罵。此外當時女學生也已經向大媽解釋了情況，但是大媽不相信。<br />\n<br />\n另上述事件發生時，火車站的警察人員已經介入控制，並請涉事大媽來見警察，接下來會依法追究大媽的責任。<br />\n<br />\n（來源於Khaosod，編譯：知否）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WeChat_20201028151341.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FWeChat_20201028151341.mp4&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=96b6895a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WeChat_20201028151341.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e6%b3%b0%e5%9b%bd%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a6%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8d%e7%ab%99%e7%ab%8b%e5%b0%8a%e6%95%ac%e5%9b%bd%e6%97%97%ef%bc%8c%e8%b7%af%e8%be%b9%e5%a4%a7%e5%a6%88%e5%bd%93%e5%9c%ba%e6%ae%b4%e6%89%93%e5%a5%b3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2F%25e6%25b3%25b0%25e5%259b%25bd%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%25ad%25a6%25e7%2594%259f%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25ab%2599%25e7%25ab%258b%25e5%25b0%258a%25e6%2595%25ac%25e5%259b%25bd%25e6%2597%2597%25ef%25bc%258c%25e8%25b7%25af%25e8%25be%25b9%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25a6%2588%25e5%25bd%2593%25e5%259c%25ba%25e6%25ae%25b4%25e6%2589%2593%25e5%25a5%25b3%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=c3527b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thaiheadlines.com/%e6%b3%b0%e5%9b%bd%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a6%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8d%e7%ab%99%e7%ab%8b%e5%b0%8a%e6%95%ac%e5%9b%bd%e6%97%97%ef%bc%8c%e8%b7%af%e8%be%b9%e5%a4%a7%e5%a6%88%e5%bd%93%e5%9c%ba%e6%ae%b4%e6%89%93%e5%a5%b3/</a>"},{"pid":"8bf92bf99006ceb9c46715d852d3cfe6c0c10b95","tid":2261421,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">人大通過修訂國旗法國徽法 港府即晚公布開展修訂工作</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-10-17 21:38<br />\n人大會議今日（17日）正式通過《中華人民共和國國旗法（修正草案）》及《中華人民共和國國徽法（修正草案）》。港府於晚上表示，《國旗法》及《國徽法》早於1997年7月1日納入《基本法》附件三，並透過制定《國旗及國徽條例》以本地立法方式在香港特區實施。特區政府會對《國旗及國徽條例》作出適當的修訂，以實施適用於香港特區的規定，履行特區政府的憲制責任。"},{"pid":"54b93790161743dec858c11e186e14b2ec456e85","tid":2261421,"uid":19126,"like":132,"dislike":4,"score":128,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"獨裁政權下特別多暴民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3681818157e6853daa7f176f5e41cfbcf70056","tid":2261421,"uid":79117,"like":5,"dislike":80,"score":-75,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24e9a0e03979c5e4ba101fa7a3881d55f016b744","tid":2261421,"uid":252960,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"廢老周圍都有"},{"pid":"5c016c3d3c68f801daad396b79fe3572dc433893","tid":2261421,"uid":26014,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"冇記錯上年6月30都有女